				%ul
					%li 5 cups of Ruby; if you don't have it you can use... PHP, Java or C# *phew*
					%li 3 cups of Rails, or if you prefer, Sinatra
					%li 1 teaspoon of Cucumber
					%li 4 tablespoons of RSpec
					%li 3 oz of Git
				%h3 Filling
				%ul
					%li 1 oz of Agile user stories
					%li 1 tablespoon of TDD
					%li several shots of Agile mindset
					%li 1 cup of pair programming
					%li half a dozen innovation desires
					%li 5 oz of problem solving
				%h3 Icing
				%ul
					%li a pinch of Heroku
					%li 2 cups of enthusiasm
					%li 1 cup of Github
					%li 3 cups of curiosity
					%li a sprinkle of startup love
					%li 4-5 gems
					%li 1 cup of jQuery
					%li 1 cup of HTML
					%li 1 tablespoon of CSS
				%h3 Decorations
				%ul
					%li 1 Pomodoro Technique
					%li 1 Bundler
					%li 1 Bash
				%p{:class => 'instructions'} Preheat oven to 350. Spray cake pans with nonstick spray and line with parchment paper; spray parchment. Sift baking Rails, Ruby and Sinatra; set aside...
